{"type":"message","id":"d1a79489","parentId":"d746c14c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:22:24.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent \"你好\" (Hello in Chinese). I need to follow the AGENTS.md startup process:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md - who I am\n2. Read USER.md - who my human is\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) - for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION - read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me start by reading these files to understand my identity and the user. The sender name is \"魏新波\" (Wei Xinbo). Let me check if there's already identity set up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是 OpenClaw 助手。很高兴见到你。让我先读取一下 workspace 中的文件，了解一下当前的情况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e9794ff4657a45cea2c11f12","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5451b749f251406dae63ae5a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c63e15f2e2f4802ada5ca62","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/BOOTSTRAP.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":9041,"output":365,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9406,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773231738289}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c7e4dc4","parentId":"d1a79489","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:22:24.345Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e9794ff4657a45cea2c11f12","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773231744342}}
{"type":"message","id":"05863fd7","parentId":"8c7e4dc4","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:22:24.350Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5451b749f251406dae63ae5a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773231744348}}
{"type":"message","id":"780558a6","parentId":"05863fd7","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:22:24.360Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4c63e15f2e2f4802ada5ca62","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773231744356}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d6746d3","parentId":"780558a6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T12:22:40.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see this is a fresh workspace with no identity or user information set up yet. According to BOOTSTRAP.md, I need to start a conversation to figure out who I am and who my user is. The sender's name is \"魏新波\" (Wei Xinbo).\n\nLet me follow the bootstrap process and have an initial conversation to establish:\n1. My name and identity\n2. Their information and preferences\n3. Our working relationship\n\nI should be friendly and natural, not robotic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"看来这是一个全新的 workspace，我还在\"出生\"阶段 😊\n\n你好，魏新波！我是 OpenClaw 助手，刚刚启动。看起来我们还没有互相认识。\n\n根据引导文档，我们需要一起聊聊，确定一些基本事项：\n\n**关于我：**\n- 你希望怎么称呼我？\n- 我是什么样的存在？（AI 助手？机器人？或者更有趣的东西？）\n- 你希望我有什么样的风格？（正式？随意？机智？温暖？）\n- 需要一个标志性表情符号吗？\n\n**关于你：**\n- 你的名字是？怎么称呼你合适？\n- 你通常用什么时区？\n- 有什么想让我记住的偏好或注意事项吗？\n\n我们可以一步一步来。或者如果你有想法，直接告诉我也行！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":9981,"output":382,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10363,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773231744358}}
