{"type":"message","id":"2547450f","parentId":"e1a2eedd","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:43:39.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要查看服务器当前性能水位。这是一个系统监控任务。我可以使用 exec 工具来运行系统命令来获取服务器的性能指标。\n\n常见的性能指标包括：\n- CPU 使用率\n- 内存使用情况\n- 磁盘使用情况\n- 网络情况\n- 负载\n\n我可以运行以下命令：\n- `top` 或 `htop`（需要交互式）\n- `vmstat`（系统整体性能）\n- `iostat`（磁盘 I/O）\n- `free -h`（内存）\n- `df -h`（磁盘空间）\n- `uptime`（负载）\n- `mpstat`（CPU 详细）\n\n或者更现代的工具如 `sar`、`dstat`。\n\n由于我不确定用户具体想了解哪些指标，我可以先运行一些基本的命令来获取系统概况，或者先询问用户具体关注哪些性能指标。\n\n考虑到这是一个直接的问题，我应该先执行一些命令来获取当前性能数据。\n\n让我先检查系统，看看有哪些可用的工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你检查服务器的当前性能状况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ca397fe0e33445848ea58b4e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 系统概览 ===\" && uptime && echo -e \"\\n=== CPU 使用 ===\" && mpstat -P ALL 1 1 | tail -n +4 || top -bn1 | head -n 20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5e05c97b162745bf9779991d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 内存使用 ===\" && free -h"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1125f59dfc2f49a595233450","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 磁盘使用 ===\" && df -h | head -n 20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8c60297f0971479b8d535c93","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 系统负载 ===\" && vmstat 1 3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":13622,"output":701,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14323,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773240209463}}
